[Student "S"]
{When NORTH agrees to \Ss, SOUTH will not stop short of a slam. 
The RKCB 4NT bid tells SOUTH that they have all five Key Cards since NORTH could hardly 
have a 2\C opening hand with no Aces.

SOUTH's 5\H bid is the Queen Ask, and NORTH's reply confirms that she holds 
the \SQ, and also has the \CK.

SOUTH figures the \S suit will run, and this should be enough for Grand Slam. He chooses 7NT.}

